  * Capture detailed logs of system events to diagnose issues and understand system behavior.  
* Health Checks:  
  * Continuously monitor the health of services to ensure they are running smoothly and efficiently.  
* Uptime Monitoring:  
  * Keep an eye on system availability to ensure services remain operational and responsive.  
* Tracing:  
  * Follow the flow of requests through your system to identify bottlenecks and optimize performance.  
* Profiling:  
  * Analyze the performance of your application in detail to identify and resolve inefficiencies.  
* Oncall Management:  
  * Ensure rapid response to critical issues with organized on-call schedules and incident management.  
* Alerting:  
