Security page

## Security with Skyhook

Protect your systems with secrets management, RBAC, SBOM, and binary authorization. Image/Video: Options \- 1\. Generic security image 2\. Service secrets section

Feature Details  
Design: Pick an icon that matches the subfeature name

* Secrets Management:  
  * Securely store and manage sensitive information like API keys and passwords to protect your applications.  
* RBAC (Role-Based Access Control):  
  * Implement fine-grained access control to ensure users have the appropriate permissions based on their roles.  
* SBOM (Software Bill of Materials):  
  * Maintain a detailed inventory of all software components to ensure security and compliance throughout your supply chain.  
* Binary Authorization:  
  * Ensure that only trusted and verified code is deployed to production, preventing unauthorized changes.

